snippet.title: Wooden Nickel - Teaser
snippet.description:
Wooden Nickel is a narrative adventure set in a frontier town of the great, remorseless Old West. 

http://visitwoodennickel.com/

An upcoming game from Brain&Brain, creators of Burly Men at Sea.
